{"word":"ὕστερος","slug":"ὕστερος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ὕστερος, α, ον</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Skt.\">Skt.</a>] ‘in a state or condition of being subsequent’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of a <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a>, as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ comp.\">comp.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adj.\">adj.</a> <b>latter,</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὁ\">ὁ</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὕστερος\">ὕστερος</a></el> the second one <b><a href='B:470 21:31'>Mt 21:31</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of a temporal moment or period<b><p class=\"pp4\"/>—<pp>α.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ nt.\">nt.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adj.\">adj.</a> used as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a>: <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ comp.\">comp.</a> <b>later <a href='B:470 4:2'>Mt 4:2</a>; <a href='B:470 21:29'>21:29</a>, <a href='B:470 21:32'>32</a>; <a href='B:470 25:11'>25:11</a>; <a href='B:480 16:14'>Mk 16:14</a>; <a href='B:500 13:36'>J 13:36</a>; <a href='B:650 12:11'>Hb 12:11</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ superl.\">superl.</a> <b>finally <a href='B:470 21:37'>Mt 21:37</a>; <a href='B:470 26:60'>26:60</a>; <a href='B:490 20:32'>Lk 20:32</a>; last <a href='B:470 22:27'>Mt 22:27</a>.<p class=\"pp4\"/>—<pp>β.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ superl.\">superl.</a> use of the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adj.\">adj.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐν\">ἐν</a> ὑστέροις ϰαιροῖς</el> in the last times <b><a href='B:610 4:1'>1 Ti 4:1</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ὑστέρησις\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ὑφαίνω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}